case.title: New to London - 22 (London)
case.text: Hi everyone, So I'm new to London and wanna meet guys to hang out with, go for drinks, dinner and whatever else happens. I'm 22 years old - blonde, tanned, size 12, 34DD, barbie-ish looks. I want to meet someone who is good looking and takes care of himself. Please add a picture to your reply and I'll send one back xx
